ons list is a monthly compilation of companies which have consistently increased their annual dividend payouts. However, since this list is only produced once per month, the data in it can quickly get out of date. Furthermore, with around 700</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1072593728/image_1072593728.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742748-dividend-champion-contender-challenger-highlights-week-of-december-8", "pub_date": "2024-12-07 08:37:35"}, {"id": "4742759", "title": "ISM Services PMI Expanded For Fifth Straight Month In November", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"project management institute concept with symbols PMI on wooden blocks\" data-id=\"1499812958\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1499812958/image_1499812958.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 